intro_body:

<p>WWF has carried out field projects in the region and the results will be used as good practice examples, with the aim of their replication in other regional protected areas. All the activities implemented by the WWF will results in:</p>
<p>We would like to know more on your examples of best practices regarding:</p>
<ul>
<li>new tourism products</li>
<li>economic benefits for the local community</li>
<li>better living conditions</li>
<li>improved national park management</li>
<li>mitigation of threats to nature conservation</li>
</ul>
<p><b>This is your site: a unique place that highlights examples of good practice and connects people across the region.</b> If you represent an institution, a non-governmental organization, or conduct research on the topics we have mentioned, <a href="mailto:natureforpeople@wwfadria.org">let us know</a>! We are already working on expanding this site in order to contain as many good examples which proves that preserved nature improves our quality of life. Add your logo to ours and create the natureforpeople.org together!</p>

